      "content": "A born-digital Metaconceptual Art work: a website built and owned by Sun & Rain Works around 2009, in connection with its Sotheby's Photographs auction engagement (sale N08533). Sun & Rain Works designates it as an associated part of the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork.",
