    {
      "type": "LinguisticObject",
      "content": "www.wtfisart.com is associated by Sun & Rain Works with the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork, in which Sun & Rain Works designates its 2009 Sotheby's Photographs auction engagement as art. The designation is an assertion by the artist.",
